And you'll pay like the Germans.

2:12:26.055 --> 2:12:28.721
Give it to me! Give it!

2:12:29.513 --> 2:12:31.635
I'm one of you!

2:12:33.971 --> 2:12:35.631
Brothers, I'm one of you!

2:12:46.346 --> 2:12:50.756
Comrade, let's light it!
Comrade, let me have a torch!

2:12:50.971 --> 2:12:52.051
Out of the way!

2:14:44.055 --> 2:14:45.335
The new one!

2:15:11.846 --> 2:15:13.755
Come on, we're going!

2:19:38.888 --> 2:19:41.840
626 VILLAGES IN BYELORUSSIA

2:19:42.096 --> 2:19:46.008
